Trivia (3)  


Overview (3)

Date of Birth

27 November
1927, Paterson, New Jersey, USA 

Date of Death

3 June
2000, Santa Barbara, California, USA       (pulmonary fibrosis)
    

Birth NameWilliam Edward Simon



Mini Bio (1)


          William Simon was born on November 27, 1927 in Paterson, New Jersey, USA as William Edward Simon. He was married to Tonia Adams Donnelley and Carol Marieanne Girard. He died on June 3, 2000 in Santa Barbara, California, USA.



Spouse (2)


               Tonia Adams Donnelley          

(2 July 1996            - 
3 June 2000) (his death)          


               Carol Marieanne Girard          

(9 September 1950            - 
18 June 1995) (her death) (7 children)          



Trivia (3)

      Father of Bill Simon.


      President of the U.S. Olympic Committee at the time of the 1984 Los Angeles Olympics.


      U.S. Secretary of the Treasury from 1974 to 1977.







